                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/81937225/">兜兜大师</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-03-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">反抗与革命 底层视角 宏观的思考需要有血有肉的详细实例来呈现本质</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
